{"data":[{"name":"88:1","price":"（使徒*よ、）圧倒的事態¹の話は、あなたに届いたか？","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5968,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「圧倒的事態」とは、その恐怖で人々を圧倒する、復活の日*のこと（ムヤッサル５９２頁参照）。","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:2","price":"その日、（不信仰者*たちの）顔は、（懲罰への）恐怖に陥っている。","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5969,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:3","price":"（それらの顔は、過酷な）労役に就き、消耗している。","arabic":"عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5970,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:4","price":"（それらは、）酷熱の業火に入って炙られる。","arabic":"تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5971,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:5","price":"（それらは、）煮えたぎる泉から、飲まされる。¹","arabic":"تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5972,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　地獄の民の飲食物については、洞窟章２９、イブラーヒーム*章１６－１７、整列者章６２－６６、サード章５７－５８、煙霧章４３－４６、ムハンマド*章１５、出来事章５２－５５、衣を纏（まと）う 者章１３、真実章３６－３７なども参照。","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:6","price":"彼らには、忌々しい植物¹しか、食べ物がない。","arabic":"لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5973,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「忌々しい植物」の解釈には、「炎の木」「ザックーム（夜の旅章６０「呪われた木」の訳注を参照）」「棘のある植物の一種」といった諸説がある（イブン・カスィール８：３８５参照）。","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:7","price":"（それらは彼らを）太らせもしなければ、（彼らの）飢えを満たしてもくれない。","arabic":"لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5974,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:8","price":"（復活の）その日、（信仰者たちの）顔は、恩恵を享受している。","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5975,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:9","price":"（それらは、）自分たちの（現世で行った）努力（への褒美）ゆえに満足している、","arabic":"لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5976,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:10","price":"高き楽園の中で。","arabic":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5977,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:11","price":"（それらは、）そこで戯言¹を耳にすることもない。","arabic":"لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5978,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「戯言については、信仰者たち章３の同語の訳注を参照（アッ＝サアディー９２１頁参照）。","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:12","price":"そこには、流れる泉がある。","arabic":"فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5979,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:13","price":"そこには、高い寝台がある。","arabic":"فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5980,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:14","price":"また、配置された杯、","arabic":"وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5981,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:15","price":"並べられた肘掛け、","arabic":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5982,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:16","price":"敷き広げられた絨毯がある。","arabic":"وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5983,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:17","price":"一体、彼ら（不信仰者*たち）は、ラクダがいかに創られたのか、見て（考え）ないのか？","arabic":"أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5984,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:18","price":"また天が、いかに上げられたのかを？","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5985,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:19","price":"また、山々がいかに据え付けられたのかを？","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5986,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:20","price":"また、大地がいかに平坦に伸ばされたかを？","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5987,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:21","price":"ならば（使徒*よ、人々に、啓示で）教訓を与えよ。あなたは教訓を与える者でしかないのだから。","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5988,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:22","price":"あなたは、彼らに対（して信仰へと無理強い）する制圧者などではない。","arabic":"لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5989,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:23","price":"但し、（教訓に）背を向け、不信仰（の固執）に陥った者は別で、","arabic":"إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5990,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:24","price":"アッラー*は彼を（、業火という）最大の懲罰で罰される。","arabic":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡعَذَابَ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5991,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:25","price":"本当にわれら*にこそ、彼らの（死後の）帰り所があるのだから。","arabic":"إِنَّ إِلَيۡنَآ إِيَابَهُمۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5992,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"},{"name":"88:26","price":"それから、本当にわれら*にこそ、彼らの（行いの）清算が委ねられているのだから。","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا حِسَابَهُم","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5993,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja"}],"chapter":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah","Chapter Al-Ghashiyah","Ghashiyah","Surah Ghashiyah","Chapter Ghashiyah","Al Ghashiyah","Surah Al Ghashiyah","Chapter Al Ghashiyah","Surah 88","Chapter 88","The Overwhelming Event","الغاشية"]}